<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="priorProvisions" id="idc3544eaf-47c4-11f1-bf59-9680b1269b87"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Prior Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Prior section 3023 was renumbered <ref href="/us/usc/t38/s5123">section 5123 of this title</ref>.</p>
</note>
